{
  "page": "High King of the First Men",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>High King of the First Men</b>, or <b>High King of all the First Men</b>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtrotd213_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtrotd213-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> is the title given to the mythical <a href=\"/index.php/Garth_Greenhand\" title=\"Garth Greenhand\">Garth Greenhand</a> in tales in which he's stated to have led the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a> in the migration from <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> into <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> through the <a href=\"/index.php/Arm_of_Dorne\" title=\"Arm of Dorne\">Arm of Dorne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=High_King_of_the_First_Men&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/High_king\" title=\"High king\">High king</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_First_Men\" title=\"King of the First Men\">King of the First Men</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=High_King_of_the_First_Men&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap